ons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/m181024m\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/993fd529731f51080599a4506afa7475?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/993fd529731f51080599a4506afa7475?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/m181024m\" class=\"reviewer-name\">m181024m</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 22, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I love this e-commerce activity in my webapp and its beautiful creation. Thank You to WOO TEAM</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Awesome</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/investitorul\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ec0e084596b1ba4d52a0f2990716d01d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/ec0e084596b1ba4d52a0f2990716d01d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/investitorul\" class=\"reviewer-name\">investitorul</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 21, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Woocommerce is a one of a kind ecommerce solution.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Out-of-the-box awesome</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"4 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"4\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/globalgazettes\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f9af2ee4b7fa705f8294cc3a676df531?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/f9af2ee4b7fa705f8294cc3a676df531?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/globalgazettes\" class=\"reviewer-name\">globalgazettes</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 21, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">   We have found WooCommerce to be wonderful for our needs with an option for most everything we were looking for.  It works fantastic with the Flatsome Theme and LearnDash.  It plays nice with other plugins.  Well formatted and attractive with our Themes different layouts.  \n   Our only disappointment was the need for plugins to handle different product listings that go beyond just simple, variable and grouped.  We would have given a 5 star rating if there was at least a text box for a customer to provide a little info as this would provide a work around for many unique product listing needs. </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">4</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/janedilkes\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5e9c156c7fbb5162f36841d7d7b0fe3d?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5e9c156c7fbb5162f36841d7d7b0fe3d?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/janedilkes\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jd <small>(janedilkes)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 22, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">4</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Good plugin for ecommerce</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thejunzhangrw\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a019a40d289ee27b558ac32584be44a6?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a019a40d289ee27b558ac32584be44a6?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/thejunzhangrw\" class=\"reviewer-name\">thejunzhangrw</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 17, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Good plugin and works like a charm.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Clumsy and unsophisticated</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/susantfl\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/541ae2f8c2a3c823107824a21ce0927c?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/541ae2f8c2a3c823107824a21ce0927c?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/susantfl\" class=\"reviewer-name\">susantfl</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 16, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Like so many Wordpress plugins, you would think this had been written about 20 years ago.  All the shop items have to be created as a wordpress page. I deleted it soon after installing, when I realised how bad it was.  But the worst thing was that several hours later I realised it had changed my default home page to its ugly shop page, which was still there even though the plugin was gone.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">4.0 update images missing</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kjrichey\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cbb474086bbe42019c94affcc92f7c24?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/cbb474086bbe42019c94affcc92f7c24?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kjrichey\" class=\"reviewer-name\">kjrichey</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 13, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I am PISSED off I have a highly trafficked store and with this last update my images are not showing up on my products. I dont want this I need the precious version or this to be fixed AS