ing=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ayek\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/a86c3ecf0bd3c4c6f887250bc1e9ec98?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/a86c3ecf0bd3c4c6f887250bc1e9ec98?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/ayek\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Ayek</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 15, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I like the UI, and relay on CF7 for years.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Radio Boxes</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/webtexweb\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/b0910bd6ae8ca415bdd83088939b709a?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://2.gravatar.com/avatar/b0910bd6ae8ca415bdd83088939b709a?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/webtexweb\" class=\"reviewer-name\">webtexweb</a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 14, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Literally in what world would anyone want words underneath checkboxes?\n\nI just want a yes/no\n\n\'BOX\' yes \'Box\' no\n\nHow is that not the default?</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">I love it.</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				By <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kubilzade\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/cee4c84b84ce3e37387ab534e119ff13?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/cee4c84b84ce3e37387ab534e119ff13?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/kubilzade\" class=\"reviewer-name\">Kubi <small>(Kubilzade)</small></a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 12, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">The best contact form </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Perfect contact form</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\